column1: #text=One day I decided that my backyard was missing something .
#text=I walked around in my backyard and decided that a tree would go perfectly in the corner .
#text=I drove to my local plant store and walked around looking at all the various trees .
#text=I read the tags and found one that would do perfect in my climate and it looked very cool .
#text=I walked up to the worker and told them I would like to purchase the tree .
#text=They loaded the tree up and I paid for the tree and drove home .
#text=I brought the tree into the backyard and set it down .
#text=I took out my shovel and dug a large enough hole for the tree .
#text=I placed the tree in the hole and filled it in with dirt .
#text=Then I took my hose and watered the tree in place .
#text=I took a step back and marveled at how wonderful my new tree looked .
